{"tid":1531180,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"執到Pokémon捉護主犬天書！","createTime":"2019-09-02T06:47:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T06:52:21.000Z","uid":259446,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3e87a7b13172479f93ac3bbf5384fad5a3bec4f0","tid":1531180,"uid":259446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T06:47:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ksdp9Rr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKsdp9Rr.jpg&h=af403be5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n地上執到寶 問天問地攞唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行行下地下有張Pokemon Go 捉護主犬天書！<br />\n唔知work 唔work 呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該可以卡一卡隻護主犬<br />\n然後就可以用精靈球黎捉咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知有無閃"},{"pid":"188b0afa14c3375a0ff959c8d874f454ee742347","tid":1531180,"uid":41583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T06:47:44.000Z","msg":"宜家係咩事？<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我哋成個9月冇行動呀！</span></span></strong><br />\n係咪要完啦我想問？<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">打咗90日，我哋終於將香港議題打到上國際層面<br />\n終於呼喚到外國勢力<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">或者會</span></span></strong>幫我哋立一條保障我哋嘅法案<br />\n正當美國準備復會，我哋竟然收聲？<br />\n你叫美國點通過呀？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">9月9日美國國會復會<br />\n全連登唔該力推9月8日再集結<br />\n一氣呵成，通過香港民主及人權法案！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HsCuBrf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHsCuBrf.jpg&h=ba764316